bullet_point.value: Wheelchair & Walker Cup Holder: Designed to keep drinks within easy reach, this cup holder for wheelchair can also be attached to wheeled walkers, rollators, and transport chairs
Premium Features: New-and-improved clamp design allows the cup holder to swivel in order to keep contents level
Quality Construction: The ultimate wheelchair and walker accessories, our universal cup holders are constructed of durable, lightweight plastic

Product Profile.tone_guidance: Maintain a clear, informative, and professional tone. Focus on accessibility, practicality, and reliability for users seeking mobility solutions.
key_attributes: Universal clamp-on cup holder for walkers, rollators, wheelchairs, and transport chairs
Fits tubing diameters from 1.6 cm to 2.54 cm
Dimensions: approximately 10 cm x 10 cm x 8 cm
Product Profile.product_summary: The Drive Medical Universal Clamp-On Cup Holder is a lightweight, durable plastic accessory designed to securely hold beverages on mobility devices such as walkers, rollators, wheelchairs, and transport chairs. Its adjustable clamp fits tubing from 1.6 cm to 2.54 cm in diameter and features a swivel mechanism to keep drinks level during movement.

title.text: Adjustable Drink Holder for Walkers, Rollators, Wheelchairs, and Transport Chairs, Universal Clamp-On, Swivel, Black, Model STDS1040S

bullets.text: Enjoy everyday convenience with a cup holder crafted from lightweight, durable plastic, designed to add minimal bulk to your mobility device while withstanding regular use.

Experience broad compatibility thanks to a universal clamp that fits tubing diameters from 1.6 cm to 2.54 cm, making this cup holder suitable for a variety of walkers, rollators, wheelchairs, and transport chairs.
Save time with a design that is ready to use right out of the box, featuring simple, tool-free installation for effortless setup on your mobility aid.
Benefit from a cup holder tailored for walkers, rollators, wheelchairs, and transport chairs, offering a secure fit and convenient access to your beverage during daily activities.
Keep drinks close at hand while on the move, with a swivel feature that helps keep contents level and a compact design that suits most standard cups and bottles.

description.text:
Designed to enhance daily independence, this cup holder offers a practical solution for carrying beverages while using mobility aids. The universal clamp allows easy attachment to walkers, rollators, wheelchairs, or transport chairs with tubing between 1.6 cm and 2.54 cm in diameter. Whether you need a mobility cup holder for adults or a stroller cup holder attachment, the clamp provides a secure fit and stability on various devices. The swivel feature helps keep your drink level, making this cup holder for spills a smart choice for active lifestyles.

Constructed from lightweight plastics, this cup holder is easy to handle and adds minimal weight to your mobility device. Its compact design accommodates most standard bottles and cups, making it suitable for a wide range of users. The cup holder wheelchair accessory is compatible with many mobility aids, ensuring your favorite beverage is always within reach. For those seeking a convenient cup holder for adults, this option offers reliable performance and a simple, tool-free installation.

The versatility of this product extends beyond mobility aids, functioning as a stroller cup holder attachment as well. From busy caregivers to individuals on the go, the cup holder comes ready to use and helps keep hydration close at hand. Experience added convenience and flexibility with a cup holder wheelchair users can depend on, backed by a 1-year limited warranty for peace of mind.
